Package de.iabg.math

Interface Summary
Matrix This interface declares basic functionality that mathematical matrices should have.
 

Class Summary
AbstractMatrix This default implementation of a Matrix provides basic methods and storage for row and column names.
DiagonalMatrix This Matrix is designed as a strictly orthogonal matrix.
RectangularMatrix This Matrix is designed as a standard fully populated matrix.
SymmetricMatrix This Matrix is designed as a mathematically symmetric matrix.
